title: BRIEF-SenzaGen: GARDskin Validation Report Submitted To Regulatory Authorities

organizations.name: gardskin validation report submitted to regulatory authorities

text:
Jan 12 (Reuters) - SENZAGEN AB:
* SENZAGEN‘S FINAL VALIDATION REPORT OF GARDSKIN™ SUBMITTED TO REGULATORY AUTHORITIES - REVEALS HIGHEST TEST PREDICTION ACCURACY IN THE FIELD
* GLOBAL REGULATORY APPROVAL AND RECOMMENDATION BY ECVAM AND OECD ON USE OF GARDSKIN IS EXPECTED IN APRIL 2019 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
